headline: 3 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: Dividend Kings have increased their dividends annually for 50 consecutive years, or longer.  Right now, Dividend Kings PepsiCo (NASDAQ: PEP), Nucor (NYSE: NUE), and Black Hills (NYSE: BKH) are all worth a closer look.  The dividend yield is around 3.4% right now, which is up near levels last seen during the Great Recession.
